arealeveltext: Wisconsin absentee ballots are returned to Municipal Clerks, not at the county level. The SHOW DROP-OFF OPTIONS button will take you to a state-level search to find your Municipal Clerkâ€™s office, where your ballot can be hand delivered. Your ballot can also be dropped at your polling place on Election Day. City of Milwaukee ballot dropboxes can be found here: https://city.milwaukee.gov/election/Voter-Info/Absentee-Ballot-Drop-Off-Sites
